<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Not Found - 404 Error</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #e4e9f2 100%);
            color: #2d3436;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #4834d4;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 #686de0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1;
            position: relative;
        }

        .error-code::after {
            content: '404';
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            opacity: 0.1;
            font-size: 150px;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #2d3436;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #636e72;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4834d4 0%, #686de0 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(72, 52, 212, 0.3);
        }

        .home-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 7px 20px rgba(72, 52, 212, 0.4);
        }

        .animate-bounce {
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            40% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            60% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }

        /* Decorative elements */
        .circles {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .circles li {
            position: absolute;
            list-style: none;
            background: rgba(72, 52, 212, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 25s linear infinite;
        }

        .circles li:nth-child(1) {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            left: 25%;
            top: 25%;
            animation-delay: 0s;
        }

        .circles li:nth-child(2) {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            left: 70%;
            top: 60%;
            animation-delay: 2s;
            animation-duration: 12s;
        }

        .circles li:nth-child(3) {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            left: 15%;
            top: 70%;
            animation-delay: 4s;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(-1000px) rotate(720deg);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .error-code {
                font-size: 80px;
            }

            .error-code::after {
                font-size: 100px;
            }

            .title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .message {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <ul class="circles">
            <li></li>
            <li></li>
            <li></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="error-code animate-bounce">404</div>
        <h1 class="title">Oops! Page Not Found</h1>
        <p class="message">
            We can't seem to find the page you're looking for. 
            It might have been moved, deleted, or never existed in the first place.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>